data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! Immaculate, better than new! Masterfully built by People's Choice Award winner Highland Homes. Move-in ready 1-owner brick home with great drive up appeal in sought after Devonshire with gorgeous club house, community pool, parks & trails and playgrounds. Recent updates include addition of matching hardwood flooring in Master bedroom & closet, dining room and living room, solid hardwood steps for the staircase, designer 12x24 porcelain tiled floor in covered patio. Master & study or 4th bedroom down, 2 bedrooms, Jack-n-Jill bath with separate vanities, large game & media rooms upstairs. Gourmet island kitchen with upgrade granite countertops and breakfast nook open to large family room adorned with stone wood burning fireplace & vaulted ceilings.  Covered patio overlooking large backyard with privacy fence.  Superbly energy efficient with low-E windows, radiant barrier roof & high SEER rated HVAC. Remainder of 10-year Builder structural warranty.
